dc_title_s: Bike, Level Of Traffic Stress, Draft Philadelphia Category 3 Connections, Delaware Valley Regional Planning Commission: Philadelphia, Pennsylvania
dct_alternativeTitle_sm: DVRPC Bike Stress DRAFT Philadelphia LTS 3 Connections
dc_description_s: ONE OR MORE OF THE ACCESS LINKS FOR THIS RECORD WERE REPORTED AS BROKEN. THE RECORD MAY HAVE BEEN RETIRED BY THE HOST. Shows all LTS 3 roads in Philadelphia. Top [x] Percent attributes show if the segment is in the top [x] percent in the city. The percentages are based on the number of connections between Census blocks that would be enabled if LTS was reduced to 1 or 2 along these segments. A value of 1 in the percentage attribute means the segment falls in that percentage, while a value of 0 means that it does not.
